        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "The princess is right. It doesn't matter who I face. All evil must be banished from Maple World."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "I won't let the problems of my people infect Maple World. I have no choice but to take down anyone who gets in my way..."
